{"url":"https://www.uokuni-s.co.jp/message/","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"ja\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0\">\n<meta name=\"format-detection\" content=\"telephone=no\">\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"おいしくてヘルシーな食事、ワクワク楽しい時間、人との豊かな交流、次世代につながるチャレンジ。これからも食と健康の新しい価値を創造していきます。\">\n<title>私たちがお届けするもの｜株式会社魚国総本社</title>\n\n<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"/assets/images/common/favicon.ico\">\n\n<link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\n<link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;500;700&display=swap\">\n\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/assets/css/style.css\">\n\n<!-- Google Tag Manager -->\n<script>(function(w,d,s,l,i){w[l]=w[l]||[];w[l].push({'gtm.start':\nnew Date().getTime(),event:'gtm.js'});var f=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0],\nj=d.createElement(s),dl=l!='dataLayer'?'&l='+l:'';j.async=true;j.src=\n'https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtm.js?id='+i+dl;f.parentNode.insertBefore(j,f);\n})(window,document,'script','dataLayer','GTM-K98Q7BWW');</script>\n<!-- End Google Tag Manager -->\n</head>\n\n<body>\n<!-- Google Tag Manager (noscript) -->\n<noscript><iframe src=\"https://www.googletagmanager.com/ns.html?id=GTM-K98Q7BWW\"\nheight=\"0\" width=\"0\" style=\"display:none;visibility:hidden\"></iframe></noscript>\n<!-- End Google Tag Manager (noscript) -->\n\n<div class=\"l-wrapper\">\n  <header class=\"l-header\"></header>\n\n  <section class=\"p-message-head\">\n    <div class=\"p-message-head__img\"><img src=\"/assets/images/message/message_head_img01_pc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"js-image-switch\"></div>\n    <div class=\"p-message-head__panel l-sec--wrapper\">\n      <h1 class=\"p-message-head__ttl\">\n        <span class=\"p-message-head__ttl--cap\">Message</span>\n        <em class=\"p-message-head__ttl--em\">私たちがお届けするもの</em>\n      </h1>\n      <h2 class=\"p-message-head__lede\"><span class=\"u-color--red1\">「驚きや感動あふれるサービスを<br class=\"u-d-none u-d-sp-block\">創造したい」</span><br class=\"u-d-none u-d-sp-block\">これからも変わらない想いです。</h2>\n      <p class=\"p-message-head__txt\">おいしくてヘルシーな食事、ワクワク楽しい時間、人との豊かな交流、明日の元気、次世代につながるチャレンジ。私たちはコントラクトフードビジネスの総合企業として、さまざまな価値をお届けしてきました。時代が変わっても、常にお客様と社会のお役に立てるように。これからも食と健康の新しい価値を創造していきます。</p>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <main class=\"l-main l-main__lower p-message\">\n\n    <div class=\"l-bread-crumb\">\n      <ul class=\"l-bread-crumb__list\">\n        <li class=\"l-bread-crumb__item\"><a href=\"/\">Home</a></li>\n        <li class=\"l-bread-crumb__item\">私たちがお届けするもの</li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <section class=\"l-main__sec p-message-detail__sec\">\n      <div class=\"l-sec--wrapper\">\n        <div class=\"c-cards c-cards__v1\">\n          <div class=\"c-card c-card__v1\">\n            <a href=\"/message/health.html\" class=\"c-card__link c-card__link--arrow\">\n              <div class=\"c-card__thumb\"><img src=\"/assets/images/message/message_thumb01_pc.jpg\" alt=\"健康の創造\" class=\"js-image-switch\"></div>\n              <div class=\"c-card__block\">\n                <h3 class=\"c-card__ttl p-card__ttl--item1\">健康の創造</h3>\n              </div>\n            </a>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"c-card c-card__v1\">\n            <a href=\"/message/safety.html\" class=\"c-card__link c-card__link--arrow\">\n              <div class=\"c-card__thumb\"><img src=\"/assets/images/message/message_thumb02_pc.jpg\" alt=\"徹底した衛生管理、安全管理、感染症対策\" class=\"js-image-switch\"></div>\n              <div class=\"c-card__block\">\n                <h3 class=\"c-card__ttl p-card__ttl--item2\">徹底した衛生管理、<br>安全管理、<br class=\"u-d-none u-d-sp-block\">感染症対策</h3>\n              </div>\n            </a>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"c-card c-card__v1\">\n            <a href=\"/message/emergency.html\" class=\"c-card__link c-card__link--arrow\">\n              <div class=\"c-card__thumb\"><img src=\"/assets/images/message/message_thumb03_pc.jpg\" alt=\"災害時などのフレキシブルな対応\" class=\"js-image-switch\"></div>\n              <div class=\"c-card__block\">\n                <h3 class=\"c-card__ttl p-card__ttl--item3\">災害時などの<br>フレキシブルな<br class=\"u-d-none u-d-sp-block\">対応</h3>\n              </div>\n            </a>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"c-card c-card__v1\">\n            <a href=\"/message/sdgs.html\" class=\"c-card__link c-card__link--arrow\">\n              <div class=\"c-card__thumb\"><img src=\"/assets/images/message/message_thumb04_pc.jpg\" alt=\"健康の創造\" class=\"js-image-switch\"></div>\n              <div class=\"c-card__block\">\n                <h3 class=\"c-card__ttl p-card__ttl--item4\">食堂を起点とした<br class=\"u-d-pc-none\">お客様の<br><span class=\"text_palt\">「SDGs推進」<br class=\"u-d-pc-none\">「ESG経営に貢献」</span></h3>\n              </div>\n            </a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"l-main__sec l-main__sec--full c-cat-nav\">\n      <div class=\"l-sec--wrapper\">\n        <div class=\"c-cat-nav__block\">\n          <h2 class=\"c-cat-nav__ttl c-cat-nav__ttl--2col\">私たちが<br class=\"u-d-block u-d-sp-none\">お届けするもの</h2>\n          <ul class=\"c-cat-nav__list c-cat-nav__list--2col\">\n            <li class=\"c-cat-nav__item\"><a href=\"/message/health.html\">健康の創造</a></li>\n            <li class=\"c-cat-nav__item\"><a href=\"/message/safety.html\">徹底した衛生管理、安全管理、感染症対策</a></li>\n            <li class=\"c-cat-nav__item\"><a href=\"/message/emergency.html\">災害時などのフレキシブルな対応</a></li>\n            <li class=\"c-cat-nav__item\"><a href=\"/message/sdgs.html\"><span>食堂を起点としたお客様の<br><span class=\"text_palt\">「SDGs推進」「ESG経営に貢献」</span></span></a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"l-main__sec l-main__sec--full c-contact\" id=\"contact\"></section>\n\n  </main>\n\n  <footer class=\"l-footer\"></footer>\n  <div class=\"l-b